            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Crush your <strong>walnuts </strong>lightly in their bag with a <strong>rolling pin </strong>(keep them in the bag so you don’t lose any!)</p><p>Tip: If you don’t have a rolling pin, just chop them roughly!</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1661183668402-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1661183668402-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1661183668402-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
