          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1661183670994-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the mushroom is cooking, dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> with your <strong>Henderson's Relish </strong>in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>Henderson's stock</strong></p><p>Once the mushroom has softened, add the<strong> Henderson's stock</strong> to the pan and cook for 1-2 min or until the stock has slightly reduced</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1661183687026-x200.jpg",
