            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1661183687026-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>quick cook spaghetti </strong>to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, then bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the spaghetti<strong> </strong>for 2-3 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>spaghetti</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
